  "heading_path": "光的衍射 / 圆孔夫琅禾费衍射与光学仪器的分辨本领",
  "intensity": "STRUCTURAL",
  "line_count": 63,
  "masked_text": "[[PROTECTED:F00001-P02594:0ccc7c713f4e]]\n\n[[PROTECTED:F00001-P02595:ff2eb9e78880]]{figure}[htbp]\n[[PROTECTED:F00001-P02596:444090bde130]]\n[[PROTECTED:F00001-P02597:ffcdd7cc9949]]\n[[PROTECTED:F00001-P02598:a95360f059e6]]{圆孔衍射示意图}\n[[PROTECTED:F00001-P02599:06b3847e1b6f]]{figure}\n\n[[PROTECTED:F00001-P02600:7d42955c2839]]\n\n[[PROTECTED:F00001-P02601:93cec519cdd6]]\n\n[[PROTECTED:F00001-P02602:ff2eb9e78880]]{figure}[htbp]\n[[PROTECTED:F00001-P02603:444090bde130]]\n[[PROTECTED:F00001-P02604:0598e0a53ba4]]\n[[PROTECTED:F00001-P02605:a95360f059e6]]{学仪器能否区分两个物点与瑞利判据}\n[[PROTECTED:F00001-P02606:06b3847e1b6f]]{figure}\n\n[[PROTECTED:F00001-P02607:dd8f12d53e6c]]\n\n[[PROTECTED:F00001-P02608:ff2eb9e78880]]{solution}\n把人眼看成一个有限孔径的成像系统。恰好能分辨时，角分辨极限满足瑞利判据：\n[[PROTECTED:F00001-P02609:f53c78951e45]]\n\n所以最远约在 [[PROTECTED:F00001-P02610:f1255fd4af98]] 处，人眼还能勉强把两盏车灯分开。这个例子说明：瑞利判据不是抽象结论，而是直接限制[[PROTECTED:F00001-P02611:0e5ea3ed8cd7]]。\n[[PROTECTED:F00001-P02612:06b3847e1b6f]]{solution}\n\n[[PROTECTED:F00001-P02613:d90695973033]]\n\n[[PROTECTED:F00001-P02614:ff2eb9e78880]]{solution}\n望远镜物镜是有限圆孔系统，能否分辨两颗星由瑞利判据控制。题目已经给出张角，所以不需要再做线距离到角度的换算。\n [[PROTECTED:F00001-P02615:c0d62240bb01]] \n张角越小，所需口径越大；波长越短，分辨越容易。最后得到的是 [[PROTECTED:F00001-P02616:7d9943310c76]]，按题意写成 [[PROTECTED:F00001-P02617:a944f05c4804]] 更直观。\n[[PROTECTED:F00001-P02618:06b3847e1b6f]]{solution}\n",
